                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960406-86-defend970 t17960406-86-punish491"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury, before Mr. COMMON SERGEANT.</p>
